body:
The main change here is to make `IMetric.java` generic and it's cascading effects. It changes from this:

```
public interface IMetric {
  Object getValueAndReset();
}
```

to this:

```
public interface IMetric<T> {
  T getValueAndReset();
}
```

With this change the metrics code will be entirely type safe, and we will no longer have java warnings from any of the codebase. This change should be backward compatible.
